{"tid":1387414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拋磚」係咪要課金支援車長 先搞得成癱瘓交通經濟","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:21:27.000Z","uid":55105,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc906a121111ce2911b56ac1c3264d92aa11174f","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"香港人冇野多 勝在錢多<br />\n之前課金登廣告話咁快就眾籌到幾球<br />\n大家明明都想車長肯帶頭罷工<br />\n但係就要佢地面對失業嘅風險<br />\n我地係咪唔應該只係犧牲佢地嘅前途咁自私？<br />\n我地係咪都應該要以行動去支持佢地？<br />\n好過日日搞不合作運動塞港鐵搞到市民<br />\n塞完港鐵 只係令到返工遲左 工又罷唔到 經濟又癱唔到 壓力又畀唔到政府<br />\n係咪課金支援車長罷工更為有效？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論 有錯勿屌"},{"pid":"9cd62f2bc5eed7bb8cf8c2927faacba5c526c24d","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fefabd903300673c5d3ada468c36ca60cab72c9e","tid":1387414,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"[個腦生屎？] 咪撚再講捐飯 、捐八達通  用下個腦啦 不服來辯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港人全部都係弱智<br />\n竟然唔從根本解決問題 買裝比前線<br />\n重話香港人好醒😨<br />\n有鬼帶頭吹風搞捐飯捐券捐錢比d不知名人士就跟<br />\n<br />\non99<br />\n#恥而為伍"},{"pid":"f675372d1efb5a56abbc9ef3ed5c07f08aaf5501","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47991a0066f2c92b7d6414a78ac73f506b6174b4","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09f2b064fa3842dcc9728d07ed21de89d4034d41","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c062f98e40736cdf24b57c79422e28761205066","tid":1387414,"uid":55105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f13a8317f1da4d152fba5bdb7714342a01c8a9d","tid":1387414,"ui